### Search for books
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search?query=harry

### Get available books with pagination
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/available?page=1&pageSize=20

### Get available books sorted by price
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/available?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc

### Get featured books
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/featured

### Get book by ISBN
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/by-isbn/123456789

### Get sellers for a book
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/sellers/123456789

### Get search statistics
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/stats

### Health check
GET http://localhost:5002/api/search/health